{"tid":1682714,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[行動po] 11月2維園見,同我推爆佢","createTime":"2019-10-30T08:31:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-31T08:15:08.000Z","uid":99003,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"81bd40400b515bb2d8a47a1dd0e28e7369b4268b","tid":1682714,"uid":99003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T08:31:06.000Z","msg":"點解連ig fb都好少人講112<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(第一次出po,個po係copy另一個手足既,見諒<br />\n輸出革命？收皮啦香港人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1682037\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1682037</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區)</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求爭取到一個就叫成功？<br />\n唔該大家見到112既行動post就推！<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好剩係講：「推！」</span></strong></span>或者係story post張相就算<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">試下講：<br />\n「11。2 維園見！」<br />\n「11。2！多你一個好多！」</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住一個重點<br />\n人越多就越安全</span></span></strong><br />\n要重現二百萬加一歷史！只係差你一個！<br />\n麻煩大家拖多個朋友出黎！唔好落單！<br />\nBE WATER!<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n睇到依度你地諗一諗<br />\n既然個個行動post推唔上<br />\n不如試下一人一post<br />\n同樣都帶到宣傳既作用<br />\n我都第一次開行動post<br />\n你地都得<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FqsntEt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFqsntEt.jpg&h=996cbf64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YZwvCxP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYZwvCxP.jpg&h=c2a30f31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7mX6Vjv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7mX6Vjv.jpg&h=3faa2803&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jdADMrb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjdADMrb.jpg&h=2f9600d5&s={SIZE}\" /><b